No. 10-9439 (10A933). Joe Teague, Petitioner v. North Carolina Department of Transportation. 563 U.S. 1002, 131 S. Ct. 2454,

179 L. Ed. 2d 1236,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 3577, May 16, 2011.

Application for stay, addressed to Justice Alito and referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certio-rari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit denied.

Same case below, 403 Fed. Appx. 872.
